\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 25
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 Each man brought his present: articles of silver and gold, garments, armor, spices, horses, and mules, at a set rate year by year. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 26
