\f1\b\fs64 \cf4 11
\b0\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 But King Solomon loved many foreign women, as well as the daughter of Pharaoh: women of the Moabites, Ammonites, Edomites, Sidonians, and Hittites-- 
